extendedInfo.description: ** THE MOST EXCITING FPS GAME â GUN N STRIKE TERRORIST ** You are a soldier on the side line protecting an army truck on the road which is being followed by enemy soldiers in jeeps, armored vehicles and other military vehicles firing at your truck. Use your big arsenal of weapons to protect your supply truck from the enemy forces. You have a AK 47 gun to stop the enemy and can also launch grenades. As you progress in this Gun N Strike game you also have to shoot down Apache combat helicopters. Test your shooting skills in this intense shooter game!DISTINCTIVE SCENES AND CHALLENGING LEVELS - There are 10 levels and each level get's tougher and tougher. - copters, tankers, choppers, and jeep trying to enter the city.IMMERSIVE GAME EFFECTS - Variety of realistic dynamic physics effectsï¼such as hit strikeï¼explosionï¼etc. - Realistic blast and best shooting game to spend some time. - A full range of weapons systems: covers let you experience the thrill of Fun variety of firearms, from pistols, submachine guns to the whole set of firearms sniper rifle, nine kinds of weapons are free for you to choose, such as Desert Eagle, AK47,SG552,M4A1,MP5,AUG,P90,M3,MAC10, etc;- Elite forces defence. Strike invading army in this casual counter attack and shoot the enemy war game. Advanced gun and rifle. If you like games like counter strike, ETERNITY WARRIORS, frontline commando then you will like this.
